{"header":"<h1>Module <code><span>Soteria.Bv_values</span></code></h1>","type":"documentation","uses_katex":false,"breadcrumbs":[{"name":"Index","href":"../../../index.html","kind":"leaf-page"},{"name":"soteria","href":"../../index.html","kind":"page"},{"name":"Soteria","href":"../index.html","kind":"module"},{"name":"Bv_values","href":"#","kind":"module"}],"toc":[{"title":"Overview","href":"#overview","children":[]},{"title":"Using the functors","href":"#using-the-functors","children":[]}],"source_anchor":null,"preamble":"<p>Extensible bit-vector based values, with floating point support. Suitable for low-level languages.</p>","content":"<h2 id=\"overview\"><a href=\"#overview\" class=\"anchor\"></a>Overview</h2><p>The core is <a href=\"Svalue/index.html\"><code>Svalue</code></a>: an untyped, hash-consed expression grammar (booleans, bit-vectors, floats, pointers, sequences, quantifiers) equipped with simplifying smart constructors. On top of it <a href=\"Typed/index.html\"><code>Typed</code></a> adds a phantom &quot;ghost&quot; type tracking the <em>kind</em> of each value (integer, boolean, pointer, ...) for extra static safety. <a href=\"Encoding/index.html\"><code>Encoding</code></a> lowers values to SMT, <a href=\"Bv_solver/index.html\"><code>Bv_solver</code></a> drives Z3, and <a href=\"Analyses/index.html\"><code>Analyses</code></a> are the abstract domain analyses used along the way.</p><h2 id=\"using-the-functors\"><a href=\"#using-the-functors\" class=\"anchor\"></a>Using the functors</h2><p>Everything is parameterised by <a href=\"Svalue/module-type-Value_ext/index.html\" title=\"Svalue.Value_ext\"><code>Value_ext</code></a>, a <em>domain-specific extension</em> that adds extra value/type leaves to the grammar. Tools that need no extra leaves pass <a href=\"Svalue/Dummy_ext/index.html\"><code>Svalue.Dummy_ext</code></a>.</p><p>A tool instantiates the typed layer <b>once</b> and reuses it everywhere:</p><pre class=\"language-ocaml\"><code>module Typed = Bv_values.Typed.Make (Bv_values.Svalue.Dummy_ext) ()</code></pre><p>From <a href=\"Typed/index.html\"><code>Typed</code></a> one then gets <a href=\"Typed/Make/Svalue/index.html\" title=\"Typed.Make.Svalue\"><code>Typed.Svalue</code></a> (the untyped layer and its constructors), <a href=\"Typed/Make/Eval/index.html\" title=\"Typed.Make.Eval\"><code>Typed.Eval</code></a> (normalisation) and <a href=\"Typed/Make/Expr/index.html\" title=\"Typed.Make.Expr\"><code>Typed.Expr</code></a> (substitution). To discharge path conditions, feed <code>Typed</code> to a solver from <a href=\"Bv_solver/index.html\"><code>Bv_solver</code></a>.</p><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec module anchored\" id=\"module-Analyses\"><a href=\"#module-Analyses\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">module</span> <a href=\"Analyses/index.html\">Analyses</a></span><span> : <span class=\"keyword\">sig</span> ... <span class=\"keyword\">end</span></span></code></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec module anchored\" id=\"module-Encoding\"><a href=\"#module-Encoding\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">module</span> <a href=\"Encoding/index.html\">Encoding</a></span><span> : <span class=\"keyword\">sig</span> ... <span class=\"keyword\">end</span></span></code></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec module anchored\" id=\"module-Eval\"><a href=\"#module-Eval\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">module</span> <a href=\"Eval/index.html\">Eval</a></span><span> : <span class=\"keyword\">sig</span> ... <span class=\"keyword\">end</span></span></code></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec module anchored\" id=\"module-Save_counter\"><a href=\"#module-Save_counter\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">module</span> <a href=\"Save_counter/index.html\">Save_counter</a></span><span> : <span class=\"keyword\">sig</span> ... <span class=\"keyword\">end</span></span></code></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec module anchored\" id=\"module-Svalue\"><a href=\"#module-Svalue\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">module</span> <a href=\"Svalue/index.html\">Svalue</a></span><span> : <span class=\"keyword\">sig</span> ... <span class=\"keyword\">end</span></span></code></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec module anchored\" id=\"module-Bv_solver\"><a href=\"#module-Bv_solver\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">module</span> <a href=\"Bv_solver/index.html\">Bv_solver</a></span><span> : <span class=\"keyword\">sig</span> ... <span class=\"keyword\">end</span></span></code></div><div class=\"spec-doc\"><p>Ready-to-use Z3 solvers over a built typed layer <code>Typed</code> (from <a href=\"Typed/Make/index.html\"><code>Typed.Make</code></a>). Each bundles SMT <a href=\"Encoding/index.html\"><code>Encoding</code></a> with the <a href=\"Analyses/index.html\"><code>Analyses</code></a>-based simplifiers.</p></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec module anchored\" id=\"module-Typed\"><a href=\"#module-Typed\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">module</span> <a href=\"Typed/index.html\">Typed</a></span><span> : <span class=\"keyword\">sig</span> ... <span class=\"keyword\">end</span></span></code></div></div>"}